<h1>
Vision</h1>
<h2>Introduction</h2>
To create a multiplayer 3d game written in java, based off the JOGL bindings..<br>
<h2>Problem/Opportunity Statement</h2>
<table>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td bgcolor="#ccffff"><font size="+1">The problem of</font>&nbsp;</td>
      <td>Creating a cross-platform 3d game</td>
    </tr>
