      <td bgcolor="#ccffff"><font size="+1">affects</font>&nbsp;</td>
      <td>potenial gamers, and developers wanting to write high performance real time code</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td bgcolor="#ccffff"><font size="+1">the impact of which is</font>&nbsp;</td>
