<blockquote> </blockquote>
<h3>Product Position Statement</h3>
<p>This engine would be as crossplatform as is possible - only very specific OS bindings need to be included, and can be packaged neatly and efficently with the jar file.</p>
<h2>Key High-Level Goals</h2>
<ul>
	<li>Create a 3d engine</li>
	<li>Network 3d engine</li>
	<li>Add fun game</li>
	<li>???</li>
	<li>Profit!</li>
</ul>
<h2>
Summary of System Features</h2>
<ul>
	<li>A window is created with a 3d maze and player controled ship</li>
</ul>
<h2>
Other Requirements &amp; Constraints</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Written in java.</li>
  <li>Requires OS specific bindings - packaged in this jar</li>
  <br>
  <li>Include supplementary specifications that span the system
(hence
do not belong within any particular user story or use case).</li>
</ul>
